{"tid":801081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【湖南直擊】一班107人交叉感染肺結核 學校政府齊隱瞞疫情","createTime":"2018-08-31T10:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T15:34:29.000Z","uid":179810,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3875821748b749d67ec37c4170488709d7ae8aef","tid":801081,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:45:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58625839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58625839&d=ZLoo38Xlgln5pGjbkuEY%2BP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bf0f0c4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58625839&h=92838816\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58625839</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n「旁邊那女同學天天咳嗽，後來去檢查，就休學了，沒有再回來......」湖南省益陽市桃江四中364班精英班女生小凡，稱她們班由80多人增至107人，去年暑假期間陸續有同學出現肺結核的病徵，她認為全班學生都應該染病。家長聘請的律師則認為，學校、疾控中心、政府都在隱瞞疫情，表示會追究責任。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n小凡稱，364精英班本來只有80多人，在校內師資最好，而且有淘汰機制，只要測試成績不達標便會被轉到普通班級，因此以往升讀大學的比例最高。不過，她說班主任不斷收家長的禮物，將未達標的學生都招到精英班，令到全班暴增至107人，上課時所有學生都擠在一起，同學出課室「要從課桌上爬出去」。初時有學生肺結核病發時，他們以為只是普通感冒，她更稱「除非抵抗力特別好」，否則全班同學都應該受感染。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n染病的學生越來越多，校方無法隱瞞疫情，於是去年8月18日要求364班停課，學生接受檢查，只有體檢合格、拿到健康證明的學生才能復課。可是，小凡稱當局安排患肺結核但停藥的學生聚在一個小班上課，結果令到教英語的年輕女老師染病，部份情況穩定的學生，亦再受感染復發。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n學生家長委托的律師團隊，打算向當局追究責任。代表律師之一陳科雲指出，他們調查所得，早在2016年，桃江四中已有2名學生病發，已可能傳染給別人，按規定曾與學生要隔離，接觸的師生、家長都要觀察，但當局卻沒有這樣做，「更荒唐是，後面許多患病學生根本沒有休學」，這導致去年8月當局對桃江四中364學生全面檢查時，疫情已經大爆發，而且擴散至湖南六個縣市和地區，除桃江縣外，包括益陽市、長沙市的長沙縣，及長沙部份地區，且疫情在今年仍出現。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「桃江學生肺結核疫情肯定是府的責任，但涉及哪一級政府負責，應由湖南省政府調查確定！」陳科雲認為，各級政府部門中、衞計部門在疫情大爆發有最大責任，特別是桃江縣疾控中心的幾名醫生，隱瞞疫情，是故意傳播傳染病源，涉危害公共安全罪，最高可判死刑。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535636384_c0a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535636384_c0a5.jpg&h=255278ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n小凡稱一班多達107人，除非抵抗力很高，否則全班都應該受感染。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"bcdb7944f501020453878042014cda28f956d0a4","tid":801081,"uid":179810,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"【湖南直擊】肺結核爆發1年 71學生仍服藥女生崩潰跳河<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58625072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58625072&d=ZLoo38Xlgln5pGjbkuEY%2BP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ce64f8fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58625072&h=5c512bba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58625072</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535636091_5aa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535636091_5aa6.jpg&h=fc5dbd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n湖南桃江學校爆發肺結核疫情後一年，家長到省教育廳，要求當局保送子女入大學。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n又到開學的日子，《蘋果》記者到湖南省益陽市姚江縣，探訪去年感染肺結核的學生最新情況。其中，「疫情」最嚴重的桃江四中，至今仍有71人需要繼續服食藥物，該校的精英班學生，治療期間不堪各種壓力精神崩潰，有人兩度企圖跳河自殺，有人一次吞下六天藥被送院搶救......可是，至今仍未有部門因隱瞞疫情遭到問責，開學前有家長為子女到處維權，甚至在湖南教育廳外露宿請願，希望國際社會能施援手。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「這藥有毒性，現在耳鳴還沒有好！」17歲的小英是桃結四中感染肺結核病情最嚴重的學生之一，她不但感染肺結核，還有盆腔結核、腸結核等，「吃了十幾種藥。結核丸一次就吃20粒，現在一天要吃七、八十粒藥」。治療肺結核藥物導致患病學生肝腎功能損傷，視力受損，聽力減退，還有人掉頭髮、全身過敏起疹等。小英初期服藥後嚴重過敏，「全身起疹子、發燒」。去年8月29日，院方一度發出病危通知。小英說，服藥不但令她肝腎功能受損害，還有月經不規律，小腹痛等多種副作用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n18歲的小羽（文中學生均為化名）也因服藥全身過敏，並因學業被耽擱而出現焦慮煩悶。去年12月，她曾一天吞下6天的藥，幸被家人發現送院搶救，救回一命。之後家長帶她四處求醫治療肺結核，今年高考時，她因仍在北京治療無法參加高考。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n兩次跳河自殺的小甜，同樣因在校被感染肺結核被逼休學半年，她亦出現情緒不穩，她與母親遭到房東、鄰居歧視，甚至被逼遷，她亦因為染病後兩度到河邊企圖輕生，幸及時被發現將她勸回。小甜治療半年後復課，今年也參加了高考，並考了505分，惜只差一分未能入讀湖南省內理想的大學，「她本打算復讀再考，但身體吃不消，只能選擇到外省讀三本大學」。<br />\n<br />\n桃江四中的364科精英班，以往升學率極高，95%學生都能升大學，不過，爆發肺結核疫情後，全班20多人復讀後參加高考，但只有7名學生考到大學，原本名列前矛的學生受服藥影響，未能進入國家重點院校，只能考上普通大學。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「要求保送！」10多名感染肺結核學生的家長代表，上周四（23日）起帶同子女，在湖南省教育廳外露宿請願，要求當局按照學生以往的成績，保送這些學生上大學，家長認為，子女都是在學校染病，「當局理應對其身體健康和學業負責」，也有家長也希望外國社會援助，讓肺結核康復者出國升學。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n在開學前夕，桃江縣當局在當地黨校，安排一個「復讀班」給肺結核康復的學生上課，可是，很多學生、家長都擔心。有家長坦言，當局安排上復讀班的學生是否真的痊癒，「我們擔心會再交叉感染啊」，深怕學生病情快要恢復，又可能要回到起點，家長說：「我們真的是承受不起了，我們的小孩更承受不起了！」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n多名家長表示，桃江衞生部門在事件中已完全喪失公信力，不相信他們講的話。家長尹先生稱，在桃江縣以至湖南省內的醫院，都對學生病情很樂觀，「或是說快治癒了，甚至說可以停藥了。但到外地醫院檢查，卻被告知不能停藥，否則前功盡棄」。他又表示，當地官員只顧維穩，一直要他不要無理取鬧，他帶女兒到北京看病，官員怕他上訪，多次致電查詢行蹤，「卻從來沒有關心子孩子病情」。"},{"pid":"7b8a47952b6360d4ad2b04da4f87f12ba2d4b606","tid":801081,"uid":143260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:48:36.000Z","msg":"中国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c52fc0da2dd8243a420eef2a777a5fd49d7dc4","tid":801081,"uid":188264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:50:45.000Z","msg":"中共:全部死晒=無事發生"},{"pid":"9c436bb72025d298a6ef722621832c6f732cf0f9","tid":801081,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9726de7d295083702dec28087bc362badf6478f8","tid":801081,"uid":177047,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"辛辛苦苦中狀元入大學又點?唔識人又無家底，結果咪又係低端人口?校方都係為佢地好，早d病死無左個夢，等佢地及早重抽"},{"pid":"9783f48a7bdab1e8c3831f9b68077930d3882605","tid":801081,"uid":35914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"107人死哂，到最後報出黎會係幾多人死咗?"},{"pid":"a84e6e64b5d596284867ff3532866d0d21e35b27","tid":801081,"uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9783f48a7bdab1e8c3831f9b68077930d3882605","tid":801081,"uid":35914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"107人死哂，到最後報出黎會係幾多人死咗?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"35個"},{"pid":"398e91a7e882febf5cb5aa58234854b4505d940d","tid":801081,"uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好痴線<br />\n老師貪污搞到班房擠迫<br />\n有病又繼續返學<br />\n爆發又隱瞞<br />\n隱瞞分開上堂又搞大疫情<br />\n病好上復課班又遇到其他人原來未病好又中招<br />\n啲藥又唔知信唔信得過<br />\n<br />\n頂唔順自殺都真係有原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df08ebc8cca76b00eeb63aeaa5cf48859a9625b","tid":801081,"uid":1221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"地獄鬼國非浪得虛名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09529678b391c87b3262216657fe3c7b944fa89a","tid":801081,"uid":161168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又入一球"},{"pid":"ec5ebd4c4c566ee8ff8a0d56e1e99382fbf5046f","tid":801081,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa8301caef678c659a96f87b505c9129bcbcead","tid":801081,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:25:41.000Z","msg":"支那滅國啦"},{"pid":"a920e0fef80d7201ab47728732313a1cf18d92f3","tid":801081,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d5416bbe6113e574ce9014b137ba196ffb711a","tid":801081,"uid":3039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"準備走晒落黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2550eb91e43a2a53ed4253a04f59eaae63d0b86","tid":801081,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"地球垃圾"},{"pid":"ca7857feda39a4e86e651c75ed67d11d1757a4f7","tid":801081,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:27:54.000Z","msg":"咁多病 支那唔死返10億8億人唔得"},{"pid":"a9f0eb36d0735fa569310f7a17ebdc3cbf0341f2","tid":801081,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/233427_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F233427_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=930d5a8a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}